- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as document embedding is often used in information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also be applicable as the proposed model involves deep learning techniques. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as convolutional neural networks are often used in computer vision tasks and the proposed model uses a similar architecture.
